Miller's or Clanton?
Here, kitty, kitty, kitty.

03:08.588 --> 03:10.522
Archie?
Huh?

03:10.590 --> 03:12.524
What do you think?

03:12.592 --> 03:17.256
Well, uh, the way
the wind is pickin' up,

03:17.330 --> 03:21.198
and with the hurricane
comin' and all, you know,
I think that-

03:21.267 --> 03:23.360
<i>Well</i>-

03:23.436 --> 03:28.931
You should probably head inland
as far as possible
and-and-and as quick as you can,

03:29.008 --> 03:31.772
and then get out of
the path of the storm too.

03:31.844 --> 03:35.405
Thanks. I mean it.
Uh, sure.

03:35.481 --> 03:38.973
<i>[ Dog Barking ]</i>
Boots? Boots?

03:39.052 --> 03:40.952
- [ Meows ]
- [ Barks ]

03:41.020 --> 03:46.322
Boface! I swear, if I didn't love that dog
so much, I'd get rid of him.

03:46.392 --> 03:48.622
Now, you're gonna be all right,
aren't you?

03:48.695 --> 03:51.596
We'll be fine.
[ Engine Starts ]

03:52.999 --> 03:55.763
[ Barking ]

03:55.835 --> 04:01.102
<i>[ Sam Narrating ]</i>
<i>Strangely enough, the thought</i>
<i>ofbeing in a hurricane...</i>

04:01.174 --> 04:04.575
<i>was somehow</i>
<i>comforting and familiar.</i>

04:04.644 --> 04:07.112
<i>I guess that's because</i>
<i>every time I leap,</i>

04:07.180 --> 04:10.445
<i>I feel that strange, unseen forces</i>
<i>hurl me wherever they want to,</i>

04:10.516 --> 04:13.280
<i>and there's nothing I can do</i>
<i>to stop them.</i>

04:13.353 --> 04:18.188
<i>So that for me, life,</i>
<i>like storms, is unpredictable.</i>

04:18.257 --> 04:20.658
She's really kind of sweet,
isn't she?

04:21.793 --> 04:25.355
Who?
[ Chuckles ]
You know who- Lisa.

04:25.431 --> 04:30.698
Yeah.
No horns, no hooves.
She's just nice.

04:30.770 --> 04:34.706
I didn't expect that, especially after
the way she kept buggin' you.

04:34.774 --> 04:40.371
"Oh, Archie, I'm so scared.
Won't you come over
and help me evacuate?''

04:40.446 --> 04:42.311
I'm not sure
she'd like to hear that.

04:44.450 --> 04:46.509
When did you know
you loved me?

04:48.721 --> 04:50.689
First time I saw you.

04:50.757 --> 04:55.319
Oh, I am glad.
Because I love you too.

04:59.232 --> 05:03.134
Still, it must have been tough.

05:03.202 --> 05:07.229
But it's just like you said-
sometimes things don't work out.

05:07.307 --> 05:10.105
